odiversity studies  but will be focused on the application of population assessment models to biological datasets  Select field trips to local restoration and conservation areas will enhance an understanding of applying these conservation principles to modern global dilemmas  Prerequisite s  BI 101  and BI 102    Back to Top   Print Friendly Page   All catalogues   2016 Virginia Military Institute  Powered by the Acalog  Academic Catalog Management System   ACMS  Mobile Site 